brief: Create a dark, high-energy gaming channel landing page for UnityWolf Gaming. Include: (1) a prominent text-based logo "UnityWolf Gaming" in the header, (2) a hero section with a bold title, short tagline, and a large "Watch on YouTube" primary CTA button, (3) social links section with icons or styled links for YouTube, Twitch, Instagram, and X/Twitter, (4) an "About the Channel" section describing the type of games and streaming schedule, (5) a "Contact" section that shows the email unitywolfgaming@example.com. Page must be responsive and look good on mobile and desktop.
